upcdb_description: Having trouble finding Baby Yoda? This Entertainment Earth Exclusive! Dark Trooper will help! Features glow-in-the-dark deco! Inspired by the Disney+ Star Wars: The Mandalorian series. Entertainment Earth Exclusive! Moff Gideon sends in the notorious Dark Troopers to capture the ultimate bounty - the  asset  known as The Child! Will they succeed? Based on Season 2  Episode 6 of the Disney+ Star Wars: The Mandalorian TV series  this exclusive Funko Pop! Vinyl figure features a Dark Trooper blasting off with a scared Grogu in hand. It even features glow-in-the-dark deco! Measuring roughly 3 3/4-inches tall  the Star Wars: The Mandalorian Dark Trooper with Grogu Glow-in-the-Dark Pop! Vinyl Figure #488 - Entertainment Earth Exclusive comes in window-box packaging. Order yours today! Grogu is known by many names - The Child  Baby Yoda  kid - but you probably know him best as the pint-sized Force-wielding hero in The Mandalorian whose origins are not completely clear.
